Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.72,0:02:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你来了\N{\rEng}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,吃吧 你是饿坏了吧\N{\rEng}There. You were hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,乖孩子\N{\rEng}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）吾必另辟一径
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:06.80,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【译注: 正在朗读《农事诗》第三卷】
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,（拉丁语）自当拔尘于世
